question: Show me all newspaper publications and magazine publications that come out weekly.
sql_query1:
SELECT Publications.title 
FROM Publications
WHERE (Publications.Print_Media = "Newspaper" OR Publications.Print_Media = "Magazine") AND Publications.Publication_Frequency = "Weekly"
sql_query2:
SELECT Publications.title 
FROM Publications
WHERE Publications.Print_Media = "Newspaper" OR Publications.Print_Media = "Magazine" AND Publications.Publication_Frequency = "Weekly"
interpretation1: List both newspaper and magazine publications where either one is issued weekly.
interpretation2: Show all the newspaper publications, in addition show only the weekly magazine publications.
